feat: narrow scope to AI-direction 保研 candidates

Per the brief's "做深做窄" guidance, narrow from generic 保研 to candidates
applying specifically to AI graduate programs. Grounded the subfield list
in 2026 reality (NeurIPS topics, PKU AI institute directions, zhihu
discussions) rather than guessing.

Form (components/ExperienceForm.tsx):
- 8 curated AI subfields: LLM/Agent/RLHF, CV (classical), multimodal/VLM,
  generative/diffusion, RL, recsys, ML theory, model efficiency
- "其他(自定义)" tail input for AI4Sci/MLSys/embodied/safety long tail
- Replaced input+datalist (invisible dropdown) with proper select + custom
  conditional input — fixes the UX bug where users couldn't see they had
  preset options

Interviewer prompt (lib/prompts/interviewer.ts):
- Added an "AI/ML 领域追问弹药库" section with two parts:
  (1) red-flag signals: missing ablations / weak baselines / no error bars
      / single-dataset / "default hyperparameters" / vague personal
      contribution — drives the model to grill on these rather than ask
      generic questions
  (2) per-subfield 追问 topics: scaling law for LLM, sampling steps for
      diffusion, sim-to-real for RL, offline-eval bias for recsys, etc.
- Tier-5 style toughened: "默认假设候选人在夸大" makes Top5 interviewer
  reject hand-waving by default
- Hardened rules: model now must drill on vague answers instead of moving
  on to the next topic
- Reference output example switched from generic ResNet question to a
  proper "0.3dB 提升是否经得起方差检验" probe

Sample generator (lib/prompts/sample.ts):
- Restricted to AI domain only
- Instructed to embed 2-3 deliberate weak points (default hyperparams /
  single dataset / weak baseline / ambiguous personal role) so the
  interviewer has real targets to attack — verified working in the smoke
  test

Repositioning across landing page + layout metadata + README:
- Title: "像 AI 顶会审稿人一样" instead of "像真实导师一样"
- Explicit "AI 方向" callout everywhere, including the why-narrow rationale
  in the README intro

